    <item>
      <title>法官阻止邮政服务对邮寄选票施加限制</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/01/us/politics/judge-trump-postal-service.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该裁决基于该服务在 2021 年法律和解中达成的协议，这是法官第二次阻止特朗普总统对邮寄投票实施新的限制。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/01/us/politics/judge-trump-postal-service.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 Jul 2026 22:12:51 GMT</pubDate>
